The paper discusses the application of spectral graph theory in supervised classification, which is a topic related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of linear regression for classification and normalized radial basis function network, which are both related to neural networks and computational neuroscience (cs.NE).
